data.description: Remember the old blueberry farm, on 4 acres, where you can pick all the blueberries you want? The seller's have added on to the existing home, making it a 3 BR, 3 BA home WITH den and library! The now, 2300 square ft home offers you TWO large Master Bedroom suites with full baths and walk in closets. Bathrooms have whirlpool tubs - ceramic tile walls. Many upgrades have been built onto this home - but you get to finish the kitchen to your taste. Must see to get a good idea. Also the home has 2 separate garages, a beautiful ramp deck leading to the entry way. Kitchen has been left for new buyers to update. (Blue Berry bushes are still producing, previous sellers had a business from them). Horses allowed. Solar Panels on the property may not convey. Roof on home has been replaced and has a transferable warranty.
